channel.title: Remixes for Matik
channel.description:
This has practically become a yearly tradition for me. @Matik made a topic where he shared some of his unfinished ideas and projects, and encouraged others to join him. I‘ve remixed two of his projects now and I’ll probably do more in the future. The originals were very catchy, and I had a lot of fun remixing them. Thank you Matik for this opportunity, hope you like my remixes! <3
001(Synth Loops): https://soundcloud.com/nicholas-diamond-64215811/thecreepermatik-synth-loops-1-dizzy-remix
006 (Future): https://soundcloud.com/nicholas-diamond-64215811/future-17-2/s-rMAxt
